## 5. RENAME MAPPING — COMMON DWH COLUMN RENAMES

When the DWH renames a column, you won't find it by exact name match. Check these
known patterns:

| DWH Column | Production Column | Source Table |
|-----------|-------------------|-------------|
| RealCID | CID | Customer.CustomerStatic |
| OpenOccurred | Occurred | Trade.PositionTbl |
| ClosePositionReasonID | ActionType | Trade.PositionTbl |
| OpenPositionReasonID | OpenActionType | Trade.PositionTbl |
| Amount_Withdraw | Amount | Billing.Withdraw |
| Amount_WithdrawToFunding | Amount | Billing.WithdrawToFunding |
| FundingTypeID_Withdraw | FundingTypeID | Billing.Withdraw |
| FundingTypeID_Funding | FundingTypeID | Billing.Funding |
| CashoutStatusID_Withdraw | CashoutStatusID | Billing.Withdraw |
| CashoutStatusID_Funding | CashoutStatusID | Billing.WithdrawToFunding |
| WithdrawPaymentID | ID | Billing.WithdrawToFunding |

Add new renames to this list as they're discovered during pipeline runs.

